             was indicted <rs id="t18320405-251-off1475" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320405-251-off1475" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320405-251-off1475" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               for stealing, on the 17th of February, 5 sacks of flour, value 15l., and 5 sacks, value 15s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320405-251-victim2135" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Jones
                  <interp inst="t18320405-251-victim2135" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
